OL,3,CPride of Britain Awards 2026:
OL,4,CNominations now open
OL,6,FToday is the national launch of the
OL,7,FPride of Britain (POB) Awards.
OL,9,FThe awards recognise everyday people
OL,10,Fand celebrate the bravery and
OL,11,Fbrilliance of those who display true
OL,12,Fgrit and determination to work
OL,13,Ftirelessly to support charities.
OL,15,FWhile celebrities attend one of the
OL,16,Fbiggest events in the showbiz
OL,17,Fcalendar, it is the real people who
OL,18,Fare the stars of the show.
