OL,3,CPride of Britain Awards 2026:
OL,4,CNominations now open
OL,6,FEach year, two fantastic fundraisers
OL,7,Fget to represent our region at an
OL,8,Fawards ceremony in London, and are
OL,9,Feven in with a chance of winning the
OL,10,Foverall ITV Regional Fundraiser of the
OL,11,FYear award.
OL,13,FLast year, the West Midlands winner
OL,14,Fwas Asha Ali Rage who founded Dream
OL,15,FChasers FC in Small Heath. She was
OL,16,Fnamed as a Special Recognition winner
OL,17,Ffor her work keeping young people away
OL,18,Ffrom gang violence and knife crime.
