OL,3,CPride of Britain Awards 2026:
OL,4,CNominations now open
OL,6,FThe East Midlands winner was John Bell
OL,7,Ffrom Huthwaite, in Nottinghamshire who
OL,8,Fwon the Fundraiser of the Year award
OL,9,Ffor his work raising awareness around
OL,10,Fmental health, and suicide prevention.
OL,12,FWho can be nominated?
OL,14,FFull terms and conditions apply;
OL,15,Fplease click here to view these.
OL,17,FTo view the privacy notice, click here.
OL,19,FTo make a nomination, please click
OL,20,Fhere to go to the Pride of Britain
OL,21,Fwebsite.
